---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Now | Anton Sten â€“ UX Lead & Product Designer"
  description="What I'm focused on right now - current projects, interests, and priorities in my life and work."
  path="/now"
  image="/images/og/now.png"
>
  <div class="page-shell">
    <section class="hero-section">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1 class="h1">Now</h1>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
      <div class="content-wrapper">
        <p class="h3">This is a now page. It's a snapshot of what's occupying my time and attention right now. Not a resume. Not an about page.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-wrapper">
        <h2 class="h2">Work</h2>
        <p class="body-lg">I'm leading design at <a href="https://summerhealth.com" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-150">Summer Health</a>, where we're building tools to help parents raise healthier kids. </p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-wrapper">
        <h2 class="h2">Writing & Projects</h2>
<p class="body-lg"><a href="/products/masteringdesignsystems" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-150">My book</a> is now available as a physical book through Amazon. It feels surreal to hold something I wrote in my hands.</p>        <p class="body-lg">I'm writing more regularly about design, product thinking, and the intersection of technology and human behavior. Some of it makes it to <a href="/articles/" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-150">my blog</a>. Some of it goes out to my <a href="/newsletter/" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-150">newsletter</a> subscribers first.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-wrapper">
        <h2 class="h2">Life</h2>
        <p class="body-lg">The Swedish darkness has arrived. It's dark by 4pm now and will be for months. Some days it's draining, other days it's cozy.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-wrapper footer-note">
        <p class="body text-muted">Last updated: November 20 2025</p>
        <p class="body text-muted">This page is inspired by <a href="https://nownownow.com/about" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-150" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Derek Sivers' now page movement</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-shell {
    max-width: 1080px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px 120px;
  }

  .hero-section {
    padding-top: 140px;
    padding-bottom: 96px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-section {
      padding-top: 120px;
      padding-bottom: 72px;
    }
  }

  .hero-content {
    display: grid;
    gap: 48px;
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .content-section {
    margin-bottom: 96px;
  }

  .content-wrapper {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 48px;
    display: grid;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .content-wrapper:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .footer-note {
    padding-top: 48px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgb(var(--color-border));
    gap: 8px;
  }
</style>
